2d waveguide test case for DDM Maxwell
--------------------------------------

* Generate full mesh (-> 'waveguide2d.msh'): gmsh waveguide2d.geo

* Partition the mesh (-> 'waveguide2d_mshcut.msh'): gmsh part.geo

* Generate the split meshes (-> 'waveguide2d_mshcut%d.msh'): gmsh split.geo

* Run the DDM solution: getdp waveguide2d.pro -sol DDM -v 0 -bin -ksp_monitor

* View solution: gmsh combine.geo